Custom Fetch
You can easily plug in your own fetch library:
import fetch from 'fetch-everywhere';
import {defaultGlobals as reduxRestResourceGlobals} from 'redux-rest-resource';
Object.assign(reduxRestResourceGlobals, {fetch});

